  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Superior Rooms</strong> are around 23-29m², sleep 2-3 people and are traditional Sassi dwellings in a cave or with a vaulted ceiling. The rooms have a living rooms area and a courtyard view or a shared terrace overlooking the Sassi of Matera. All rooms have private bathrooms, air conditioning, satellite TV and internet access. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Standard Rooms</strong> are about 19-22m² and have a shared terrace. They sleep two people are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are about 30-35m² and sleep 2 - 3 people. These traditional rooms have a terrace, Jacuzzi and views of Matera. They are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Standard Single Occupancy Rooms</strong> are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Superior Single Occupancy Rooms</strong> are available on request, please call to book. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
